name: ext-net-protos-c
description: HTTP/2 + WebSocket + gRPC helpers, pinned by arch/net contracts.
docs:
HTTP/2 + WebSocket + gRPC helpers pinned by arch/net contracts.

Modules:
- std.net.http2
- std.net.ws
- std.net.grpc
- std.net.protos.tests

Worlds:
- run-os / run-os-sandboxed only

Usage:
- Add dependency: x07 pkg add ext-net-protos-c@0.1.1
- Use *_from_arch_v1 helpers with config under arch/net.
